      <title>苹果中国 iPhone 出货量因大幅折扣上涨 40%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/apple-s-china-iphone-shipments-jump-40-after-steep-discounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管在六月购物节前几周各大零售商都推出了大幅折扣，但苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 5 月份在中国的 iPhone 出货量仍增长了 40%，增幅低于上个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/apple-s-china-iphone-shipments-jump-40-after-steep-discounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 09:45:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称丰田将在上海设立独资雷克萨斯工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/toyota-said-to-seek-wholly-owned-lexus-factory-in-shanghai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，丰田汽车公司正在与上海有关部门讨论建设一家独资工厂的可能性，但在这家日本汽车制造商在中国陷入困境之际，这将是一次冒险的举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/toyota-said-to-seek-wholly-owned-lexus-factory-in-shanghai</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 09:28:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>机场、学生援助服务机构遭受印尼网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/airports-to-scholarships-crippled-in-indonesian-cyber-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚议会严厉谴责政府再次发生的网络攻击，该攻击导致机场和奖学金服务中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/airports-to-scholarships-crippled-in-indonesian-cyber-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 08:04:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国长鑫存储母公司将投资 24 亿美元建设新芯片工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/parent-of-china-s-cxmt-to-invest-2-4-billion-in-new-chip-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国顶级芯片制造商长鑫存储技术股份有限公司的控股公司将投资不少于 171 亿元人民币（24 亿美元）在上海建设一座先进封装工厂，可用于生产 AI 存储器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/parent-of-china-s-cxmt-to-invest-2-4-billion-in-new-chip-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 08:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渤海租赁正在洽谈至少 10 亿美元民间贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/bohai-leasing-in-talks-for-at-least-1-billion-private-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，渤海租赁有限公司正在与金融机构进行初步谈判，以筹集至少 10 亿美元的私人贷款用于再融资目的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/bohai-leasing-in-talks-for-at-least-1-billion-private-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 07:50:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国三峡集团投资110亿美元建设沙漠电力项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/china-three-gorges-invests-11-billion-in-desert-power-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国三峡可再生能源集团有限公司是中国最大水力发电企业的子公司，该集团将投资 800 亿元人民币（110 亿美元）在内陆一个主要清洁能源基地扩建其太阳能和风能发电厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/china-three-gorges-invests-11-billion-in-desert-power-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 07:42:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾即将对 Netflix、HBO 订阅征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/philippines-moves-closer-to-taxing-netflix-hbo-subscriptions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾立法者批准了一项联合法案，提议对 Netflix、HBO 和 Disney 等外国数字服务征税，旨在确保新的政府收入来源来资助额外支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/philippines-moves-closer-to-taxing-netflix-hbo-subscriptions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:38:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银在海外融资 18.6 亿美元，加大对人工智能的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/softbank-raises-1-86-billion-overseas-as-it-boosts-ai-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团公司通过发行美元和欧元债券筹集了约 18.6 亿美元，这是今年日本公司最大的外币交易之一，该科技公司正在加大对人工智能领域的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/softbank-raises-1-86-billion-overseas-as-it-boosts-ai-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:11:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
